19,"updated_time":1546087419,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得你的想法和下图得想法差不多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cf4bceb3b2b5b63a93a710297fc5789e_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"440\" data-rawheight=\"2947\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ac7d66556764666ccbfefc404750f805_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cf4bceb3b2b5b63a93a710297fc5789e_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='440'%20height='2947'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"440\" data-rawheight=\"2947\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-ac7d66556764666ccbfefc404750f805_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"440\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cf4bceb3b2b5b63a93a710297fc5789e_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-cf4bceb3b2b5b63a93a710297fc5789e_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559834094,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"10680d7a68a0381574f03a7b39787da2","url_token":"simonfiona","name":"西北望","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/c1243f315f8ed5e34478168b9994a0e3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/c1243f315f8ed5e34478168b9994a0e3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/10680d7a68a0381574f03a7b39787da2","user_type":"people","headline":"机灵的小呆逗","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559834094","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545787081,"updated_time":1545787081,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":19,"content":"\u003cp\u003e证明0.99999…=1有很多种方式\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第一种：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1/3 = 0.333...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e两边乘3   \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3*1/3=3*0.333...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e得出\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1=0.999…\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第二种：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ex=0.999...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e10x=9.999...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e9x=9\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ex=1\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想也就是停留在这个段位上的证明吧\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561954834,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fa0b7afd4910d4ab27894c639d7a253e","url_token":"ashesone-26","name":"星白闲","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-57d06c97dd46a79bce1cd890f14880c0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-57d06c97dd46a79bce1cd890f14880c0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fa0b7afd4910d4ab27894c639d7a253e","user_type":"people","headline":"白门楼上挂满了吕布的尸体","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561954834","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546021550,"updated_time":1546021550,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e数学系学渣强行回答一次\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你要是能在高中毕业前，也就是18岁前，证明哥德巴赫猜想，并且得到学术界认可\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那清华北大肯定会抢着你去\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当教授的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我本科的学校在美国算不上最顶尖也算是名校了，你让我们学校数学院本科毕业生，随便挑，保证都能看得懂问题啥意思，这算是个进步，因为我们有时候题目都能看的一脸懵逼，但是你让我们别说开个头，连找个稍微点的思路去尝试证明都不可能\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感觉题主是被民科洗脑了，看的懂就觉得应该能解出来的问题，只存在于你上学考试的时代，对于真正的数学难题一点概念都没有，18岁前能靠自己证明哥德巴赫猜想，你去清北当教授，都属于为国家牺牲小我了，你这个智力要是再高点，都能被5常抢着去研究了，完全超出人类范畴了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559467935,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559467935","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e207385b806d8cb998df0e3ded6e0f10_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545729502,"updated_time":1545730225,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e919ed8b142a826e3c094876a38b7f7b_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"290\" data-rawheight=\"302\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e919ed8b142a826e3c094876a38b7f7b_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"290\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='290'%20height='302