"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bbb58b3cf74a5fa7e835c0358e430acf","url_token":"warmwine","name":"温酒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50617f64221aac69a4e586124cc04421_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50617f64221aac69a4e586124cc04421_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bbb58b3cf74a5fa7e835c0358e430acf","user_type":"people","headline":"微信公众号:hearmr333   公众号名称：\"温酒说\"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561445618","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545968163,"updated_time":1545968189,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得可能王子屯大学会召唤你\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557294829,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0c39dee3bf4347415d4bcf08397a9866","url_token":"da-po-sha-guo-wen-dao-di-94-55","name":"打破砂锅问到底","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-83aedf6e28c074ca7b934779dcd7215d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-83aedf6e28c074ca7b934779dcd7215d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0c39dee3bf4347415d4bcf08397a9866","user_type":"people","headline":"真理，永远追求，永远不近，每揭开一层，都会引发我的狂喜","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557294829","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545456040,"updated_time":1545456338,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"content":"\u003cp\u003e      觉得你很有信心，不知道你的水平怎么样，但是你可以试试。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你成功了，祝贺你在数学界站在了无数数学家的前头。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没成功，也不会有人记得你的笑话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是我希望你能从最基础的地方开始论证，数学不是靠想象，而是严格的逻辑命题，一个地方有问题就是整个理论的崩塌，所以望你能将自己的思维缕清，再找找自己的漏洞吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是你只是将其作为一个上名校的途径，你就错了。因为你这么想的话，实际上是用最困难的方法上清华，如果你真有解出哥德巴赫猜想的能力，那就要考虑清华是否配的上你这种数学大师了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e摆正态度吧，觉得做的对你就去做，错了就改。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560111555,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b36b695f4393bc9f624d04c70b451387","url_token":"cheng-hao-peng-70","name":"鹏鹏","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/81a9662305c2e5235e4acca4e7629b57_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/81a9662305c2e5235e4acca4e7629b57_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b36b695f4393bc9f624d04c70b451387","user_type":"people","headline":"九乡河文理学院搬砖专业在读","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560111555","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545810129,"updated_time":1545810129,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e讲真，真要比一下的话，可能考上清北更容易一些。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562535130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b7495a21eea6c4353196a4d90a5d2aa2","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562535130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546097760,"updated_time":1546097760,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主你还是太弱了，我小学四年级的时候由一道竞赛题引申出发“证明”了哥猜... 虽然回家仔细思考发现只证明了一部分经过特殊构造的数满足条件（具体怎样我忘了，我的竞赛水平自那以后再也没增长过，现在也挺后悔的）。中二时期谁都有过，而你能获得的不是知乎骗来的粉丝，保送北大清华出人头地...\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而是那份数学带给你的纯粹的快乐，倾心解题的专注，完成书本知识后自由思考的自信与骄傲。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使我们变成瞟一眼数学书就去刷手机、翘微积分课打游戏的大学生，变成油腻的中年大叔，做着与数学不相干的工作，我依然记得并不后悔做那个课间颤抖着把自己的“证明”递给老师的小男孩。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e醒醒吧、不要玷污了这份纯粹，也不要放弃一些你本该能得到的教训。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=220\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=180\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
